A major issue effecting the game is that riot always take the easy route rather than rolling up the sleeves and doing some serious balance changes during the preseason or midseason.

case and point {{item:3076}} {{item:3075}} 

rather than dealing with ADC lifestealing which was completely broken at the time they reworked these items and it completely fucked toplane AA reliant bruisers which in turn lead to conqueror being added to the game

And even then they don't want pure tanks to feel good about building it since it has a coldsteel passive that doesn't stack with {{item:3143}}


Tanks complained about being healthpools for adcs to leach off of , and now this item is no longer a tank item, it feels more oriented for bruisers than tanks with the exception of taunt reliant tanks like rammus/galio who are basically bruisers at this point since everyone is made of paper.


Remember when riot was gonna make vayne heal based off of her target`s max hp when she gets a kill? Riot was really aiming to make tanks feel worse lol.
